Feature: 2.1.1 Intuitive UI
  The system shall provide an intuitive user interface. 

Feature: 2.1.2. Reactive UI
  The system shall support common display devices like 
  phones, tablets, and web browsers. 

Feature: 2.1.3. Dark and Light Modes
  The system shall provide a light mode / dark mode toggle 
  which changes the theme of the entire client UI. 
